        comparaisonTransport: "There is no direct rail service from Bordeaux to Blaye. The TransGironde bus (line 201) connects Bordeaux to Blaye in 1h15 for €2.50, but with only 5 departures daily and no service to wine châteaux. By car, the journey is nearly free (€3 toll, €5 fuel). The TaxiNeo taxi at €65 — €85 offers door-to-door, the flexibility to combine citadel and vineyard, and space to bring back wine. For 3-4 passengers, it is €16-28 per person — excellent value for a cultural and wine excursion.",
