          { question: "Can I combine Bayonne and Biarritz?", answer: "Yes, Biarritz is just 8 km from Bayonne (15 min). We offer a Biarritz stop for a minimal supplement, or a full-day Bayonne + Biarritz + Espelette circuit." }
